verse_content.Word_by_word:
pitā—father; asi—You are; lokasya—of all the world; cara—moving; acarasya —nonmoving; tvam—You are; asya—of this; pūjyah—worshipable; ca—also; guruh—master; garīyān—glorious; na—never; tvat-samah—equal to You; asti —there is; abhyadhikah—greater; kutah—how is it possible; anyah—other;
loka-traye—in three planetary systems; api—also; apratima—immeasurable;
prabhāva—power.
